# Repo-wide ignores. Each sub-project (skills/superlooper, dashboard) also carries its own
# .gitignore for the files specific to it (e.g. the dashboard's per-user config.json and
# runtime state) — git honors those per-directory, so they still apply inside their folders.
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
*.tmp
